				\begin{document}$$^{222}\hbox {Rn}$$\end{document} concentration in a DARWIN-scale detector optimized for hermetic operation depends on various parameters, which describe the 222Rn\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
